    <p class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-on-surface mb-8 italic">"DevCommand didn't just build our app; they engineered a business solution. The attention to technical detail is unmatched in my 10 years of hiring developers."</p>
    <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4">
      <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full overflow-hidden border-2 border-primary">
